merb-jquery
===========

Makes it easy to use jQuery in your application.

$ gem install merb-jquery

Add
  require 'merb-jquery'
to your init.rb

$ rake merb:jquery:install
Installs the latest jQuery to public/javascripts

In your layout, inside <head>:

<%= jquery %>


In your views:

<% jquery do %>
  $('#foo').something();
<% end %>